---
title: Sticky Sweet Chilli & Double Sriracha Beef Bowl with Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Soy sauce, sweet chilli sauce and sriracha come together on tender beef strips for the perfect balance of salty, sweet, spicy and sticky. Pair it with flavourful rice, a fresh and creamy slaw, and some crunchy peanuts for garnish, and you’re on to a winner!
